## Mermaid Diagram Templates

### Sequence Diagram:
```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant API
    participant DB
    
    User->>API: Request
    API->>DB: Query
    DB-->>API: Result
    API-->>User: Response
```

### Architecture Flowchart:
```mermaid
flowchart TB
    START([User Request]) --> AUTH{Authenticated?}
    AUTH -->|Yes| PROCESS[Process Request]
    AUTH -->|No| DENY[Deny Access]
    PROCESS --> DB[(Database)]
    DB --> RESPONSE[Return Response]
```

### State Diagram:
```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle
    Idle --> Processing: Start
    Processing --> Complete: Success
    Processing --> Failed: Error
    Failed --> Idle: Retry
    Complete --> [*]
```

